ns in the flow of speech, classified under F98.5 in the ICD-10 coding system\"", "SUBSTANCE ABUSE:Substance abuse is a maladaptive pattern of substance use leading to significant impairment or distress, as defined in DSM-Ⅳ", "SUBSTANCE DEPENDENCE:Substance dependence can result from attempts to self-medicate anxiety in social anxiety disorder"], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-v3"}}}